						               													<description>Swarnim Vijay Varsh&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On 16th December 1971, the Indian Armed Forces secured a decisive and historic Victory over Pakistan Army, which led to the creation of a Nation - Bangladesh and also resulted in the largest Military Surrender after the World War - II. &amp;#10;Vijay Diwas is celebrated every year on December 16 to mark India&amp;rsquo;s triumph in liberating Bangladesh from Pakistan in 1971. In one of the fastest and shortest campaigns of military history, a new nation was born as a result of the swift campaign undertaken by the Indian Armed forces. To commemorate this victory, from 16 December 2020, the Nation is celebrating 50 Years of India-Pak War, also called &amp;lsquo;Swarnim Vijay Varsh&amp;rsquo;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;About the Game&amp;#10;&amp;#10;16.12.1971 &amp;ndash; Is a war game designed to commemorate 50 years of India&amp;rsquo;s victory over Pakistan. Swarnim Vijay Varsh is being celebrated and we have designed it with a total of 50 spaces (50th Anniversary) in the game board.&amp;#10;The name of the game 16.12.1971 indicates: -&amp;#10;16     &amp;ndash;     Total hours taken by us to plan, design, conceptualize, play test and complete!!&amp;#10;12     &amp;ndash;     Number of Assets and Number of Targets in the game&amp;#10;1     &amp;ndash;     One Board&amp;#10;9     &amp;ndash;     Number of Challenges / Actions confronted by players / Force&amp;#10;7     &amp;ndash;     Number of Joint operations planned in the game&amp;#10;1     &amp;ndash;      One Dice&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules &amp;amp; Regulations:&amp;#10;The Print &amp;amp; play game consist of three forces &amp;ndash; Army, Navy and Airforce each with 4 assets. Each force will be navigated by three players by rolling the dice and get each of their assets(pawns), to reach the &amp;lsquo;KILL ZONE&amp;rsquo;. Once the asset is in Kill Zone, the player will Roll the dice, if lucky HE/SHE will hit the respective equivalent enemy force Target.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
